        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(byteplus): add missing cacheRead/cacheWrite pricing for BytePlus models",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nSeveral BytePlus/Doubao models in `extensions/byteplus/openclaw.plugin.json` had `cacheRead: 0` and `cacheWrite: 0` in their cost config, causing context caching costs to be underreported. This fix sets `cacheRead` to 25% of input price and `cacheWrite` equal to input price for affected models, matching the typical Volcano Engine ARK API caching pricing model.\n\nFixes #54157\n\n## Tests and validation\n\nModel catalog tests pass with updated pricing.\n\n## Risk checklist\n\nDid user-visible behavior change? (`No` — cost tracking improvement only)\nDid config, environment, or migration behavior change? (`No`)\nDid security, auth, secrets, network, or tool execution behavior change? (`No`)\n",
